# Legal Research Chatbot

An AI-powered Legal Research Chatbot that helps users find legal information through natural language queries.

## Features
- Legal information retrieval
- Natural Language Processing (NLP)
- User-friendly interface
- Fast and accurate responses

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Hugging Face Transformers
- Gradio
- Machine Learning

